metadata.description: Velocity Financial, Inc. operates as a real estate finance company in the United States. It primarily originates and manages investor loans secured by 14 unit residential rental and small commercial properties. The company offers its products through a network of independent mortgage brokers. Velocity Financial, Inc. was founded in 2004 and is headquartered in Westlake Village, California.
